🔹 Summary of Responsibilities

Feature packages (user, product, category, cart, order, payment) → handle domain logic for that object.

Each feature contains:

entity → database table

dto → input/output for API

mapper → entity ↔ DTO conversion

repository → database access

service + impl → business logic

controller → REST endpoints

security → handles auth, JWT, role-based access

config → global configuration for CORS, mapping, API docs

common → utilities, exceptions, helpers